>         ** REQUIRES:    ${c -(}d_raw{c )-}/Ecuador_F2F_Household_Raw_`cdate'.dta
>                                         ${c -(}d_raw{c )-}/Ecuador_F2F_Roster_Raw_`cdate'.dta
